The deeper abstraction

What you are really building is:

a machine for converting constrained choices into latent human structure

That means the engine is useful anywhere people reveal themselves through tradeoffs.

That includes:
	•	attraction
	•	taste
	•	loyalty
	•	aesthetics
	•	consumption
	•	values
	•	trust
