Clean final formulation

The algorithm in one sentence

Model human choice as repeated pairwise or ranked tradeoff events, enrich each event with context and metadata, infer latent preference vectors and tradeoff weights, then fuse those across domains to generate predictive and interpretable behavioral insights.

